### Multi-Tenant SaaS API - Billing
### VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client compatible

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get tokens first by running auth.http login
@accessToken = {{$dotenv %ACCESS_TOKEN}}
@tenantId = {{$dotenv %TENANT_ID}}

### Get billing overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Get plan limits
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing/limits
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Check quota for a specific resource
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing/quota/seats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Check API calls quota
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing/quota/api_calls
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Check storage quota
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing/quota/storage_gb
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
